title: VA Indie Pop August 2013 - Just Enough (Dutch Treat I1 HQ)
description:
A quite definite preview of the sixth Dutch Treat Indie Playlist of August 2013.

A funny thing happened. When I heard the first accords of Slow Summits (2), I immediately thought of a fifty year old song of Soft Machine. When playing it again, it sounded still fresh (the sound a bit less) so I simply had to include it in the list (1) (i like experiencing some musical roots).
 
And because August was a bit diffecult (supply) I had to smoggle a bit and included some older songs that sounded new to me.... Enjoy
